title: 131: Trade talk, Rodgers back on track and pass rushing keys
itunes:title: 131: Trade talk, Rodgers back on track and pass rushing keys
description:
Former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks discuss why the New England Patriots traded linebacker Jamie Collins, how Aaron Rodgers has rebounded this season, and also the keys to rushing the passer and finishing off with a sack. The duo also continue to add to their "Good player, bad body" roster.
